Ensure you fill and cross-examine the data inputed by you as you are at liberty to omit any and even all fields
{keys.map((name, index)=>{ let title = name.replaceAll("_", " "); if(name == "public_domain") title += " (Yes or No)" if(name == "has_vocals") title += " (Yes or No)" if(name == "explicit") title += " (Yes or No)" if(name == "cue_type") title += " (Instrumental or Vocals)" if(name == "tempo") title += " (Slow, Medium, Fast, etc.)" if(name == "bpm") title += " (Beats per Minutes)" if(name == "instrument_type") title += " (Band, Guitar)" if(name == "writer_PRO_affiliation") title += " (BMI)" if(name == "IPI_number") title += " (Yes or No)" if(name == "public_domain") title = ("Writer CAE/"+ title + " (Comes with PRO website)"); return })}
) }
